		<title type="text">King Lear</title>
		<content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This month I am mostly interested in art and Shakespeare. The Royal Academy&#8217;s annual <a
href="http://www.royalacademy.org.uk">Summer Exhibition</a> on TV has inspired me to get back to my roots and get messy.
Then seeing the <a href="http://www.rsc.org.uk" title="Royal Shakespeare Company">RSC</a> performance of <a
href="http://www.rsc.org.uk/newsandevents/events/5375.aspx">King Lear</a> reminds me of how much I love to watch
Shakespeare&#8217;s plays performed live on stage. <a href="http://www.staffordfestivalshakespeare.co.uk">Much Ado About
Nothing</a> is next, on an outdoor stage at Stafford Castle, always a treat. We are going on the last night to experience
all the fireworks and fun.</p>]]></content>
