		<title type="text">A Modern Classic</title>
		<content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The <a
href="http://www.ducati.com/en/bikes/my2007/ModelPage.jhtml;jsessionid=E20SOTHTWRTDKCRNCB2SFFAKFUIHUIV4?family=Superbike&amp;model=SBK1098STRICOLORE-07">new
Ducati 1098</a> is available now. A fantastic looking bike and perhaps another design classic from Ducati. It&#8217;s the
replacement for the &#8216;not so popular&#8217; 999 and to regain it&#8217;s appeal has similar features to the 916 range
of bikes produced between 1994 and 2002. I want one, but they ain&#8217;t cheap, especially the 1098 S Tricolore shown
below.</p>]]></content>
